extendedData.value:
The "Underworld Herald" deck combines aggressive swarms of creatures with devastating spells that destroy your opponents forces. Enchantment creatures and powerful devotion creatures give you a solid backup plan if your initial offensive cant finish things off.

Each event deck contains a preconstructed 60-card deck, 10 rares, and a 15-card sideboard.
